To the worm that first gnawed on the cold flesh of my corpse, I dedicate, as a fond remembrance, these posthumous memories.1




ASSIS, M. Memórias póstumas de Brás Cubas [The Posthumous Memoirs of Brás Cubas]. São Paulo: Companhia das Letras, 2014. ISBN 978-85-438-0163-6. :::↩︎
